Several Apache Server releases over the past year have not been announced to the announce@httpd.apache.org<mailto:announce@httpd.apache.org> mailing list

See the archives at:
https://lists.apache.org/list?announce@httpd.apache.org

2.4.53 was announced in March of this year
2.4.50 was announced in October, 2021

However, each of 2.4.51, 2.4.52, and 2.4.54 were not announced.

Can I please ask for the person or people who are responsible for the releases to make sure that they also announce the releases on the announce@ mailing list.

Thank you in advance,
Steve Bush


